Lim-Plugin-ZFM - Zone File Manage plugin for Lim

ABOUT

This plugin manage zone files via Lim that are file based. Since you configure
where the zone files are it can work with any software that uses file base zone
files. Support for other medias (such as databases) can be implemented in the
future.

For available RPC calls and CLI commands please see:

	perldoc Lim::Plugin::ZFM

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Lim::Plugin::ZFM

You can also look for information at:

    Issue tracker (report bugs here)
        http://github.com/jelu/lim-plugin-zfm/issues

    GIT repository
        http://github.com/jelu/lim-plugin-zfm


